      "comment": "CLAIRE KEEPING (1) turned in a moderate effort last time when eighth at this track over 300m behind Ripple Rhythm (18.36) in a Grade 6. Can discover winning form. ELITE EMU (3) is racing well without winning, recording three minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (23.02) over 400m at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Well-placed to take this out. PIGGY PARKINSON (6) turned in a solid run last start over 300m at this track finishing 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (17.96). In the mix. FREESPOOL (2) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone.",
